Not what I expected! Ending was abrupt and choppy - dethroned king disappeared? jejuwon survived despite Japanese takeover? main couple will build their own hospital/school? how? where's $ and support?

A very entertaining and thrilling historical drama. Very good acting, well written and directed story with interesting characters and nail-biting plot twists . After the first episode the story starts rolling and you are hooked. This drama has delightfully high production values, the horribly tacky dvd cover does not give a realistic image of the drama at all.

Great historical drama and wonderful medical information for the naive. A bit graphic at times, but it is brief scenes of various medical operations or conditions, so it adds to the realistic value of the film.
